OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear and
OL,6,Fdry night to come with some isolated
OL,7,Fshowers in the far southeast. Patchy
OL,8,Fcloud in parts of the west and north
OL,9,Fjust before dawn. Slightly cooler in
OL,10,Fthe west, but still warm in the east.
OL,11,FFeeling muggy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FDry, bright and hot to start
OL,14,Fthe weekend. Staying very hot but
OL,15,Ftemperatures slightly down on recent
OL,16,Fdays.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
